import React from 'react'
import Home from './pages/Home'
import Header from './components/Header'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'

function App() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
    <Routes>
      <Route path='/' element={<Header/>}>
        <Route index element={<Home />}/>
        <></>
      </Route>
    </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App
